name: TheOfficeQuotes
0:
”Alexa, open The Office Quotes”
”Alexa, tell The Office Quotes to tell me an office quote”
”Alexa, ask The Office Quotes for a quote”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: the office quotes
des: Love "The Office?" This skill will bring your favorite quotes right to Alexa. The Office Quotes will tell a random quote, along with the speaker, season number, episode number and episode title.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
